Detailed Description

Type define for a Mass Storage class Command Status Wrapper, used to wrap SCSI responses for transport over the USB bulk endpoints from the device.

Field Documentation

uint32_t CommandStatusWrapper_t::DataTransferResidue

Length of data not transferred

uint32_t CommandStatusWrapper_t::Signature

Command status signature, always equal to CSW_SIGNATURE

uint8_t CommandStatusWrapper_t::Status

Command status, a value from the MassStorageHost_CommandStatusCodes_t enum

uint32_t CommandStatusWrapper_t::Tag

Current CBW tag, to positively associate a CBW with a CSW
